<!-- Definition and symptoms -->'''膽石症'''（{{lang-en|cholelithiasis}}）是指膽囊中有结石的状态或由胆囊结石引起的任何疾病<ref name=NICE2014>{{cite journal|last1=Internal Clinical Guidelines Team|title=Gallstone Disease: Diagnosis and Management of Cholelithiasis, Cholecystitis and Choledocholithiasis. Clinical Guideline 188|date=October 2014|pmid=25473723|page=101}}</ref>。'''膽結石'''（{{lang-en|choleliths, gallstones}}）则是在[[膽囊|膽囊]]內由[[膽汁|膽汁]]成分沉淀而生的[[结石|结石]]<ref name=NIH2013/>。大多數膽結石患者（約80%）不曾有過症狀<ref name=NIH2013/><ref name=Lee2015>{{cite journal|last1=Lee|first1=JY|last2=Keane|first2=MG|last3=Pereira|first3=S|title=Diagnosis and treatment of gallstone disease.|journal=The Practitioner|date=June 2015|volume=259|issue=1783|pages=15–9, 2|pmid=26455113}}</ref>。膽結石的患者中，有1-4%每年發生[[腹部|腹部]]右上方痙攣疼痛，稱為{{le|膽道絞痛|Biliary colic}}<ref name=WS2016/>，膽結石併發症包含[[膽囊炎|膽囊炎]]，[[胰腺炎|胰腺炎]]和[[肝炎|肝炎]]<ref name=NIH2013/><ref name=WS2016/>。這些併發症可能導致持續超過五小時的疼痛、[[發燒|發燒]]、[[黄疸|黄疸]]、嘔吐或[[尿液|尿液]]呈現茶色等症狀<ref name=NIH2013/>。

<!-- Cause and diagnosis -->
膽結石的危險因子包括[[避孕藥|避孕藥]]，[[懷孕|懷孕]]，膽結石家族史，[[肥胖症|肥胖症]]，[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]，{{le|肝病|cirrhosis}}或快速減肥。<ref name=NIH2013/>膽結石在膽囊形成，通常來自[[膽固醇|膽固醇]]或[[膽紅素|膽紅素]]。<ref name=NIH2013>{{cite web|title=Gallstones|url=https://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/health-topics/digestive-diseases/gallstones/Pages/facts.aspx|website=NIDDK|accessdate=27 July 2016|date=November 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160728005016/https://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/health-topics/digestive-diseases/gallstones/Pages/facts.aspx|archivedate=2016-07-28}}</ref>由症狀可推論可能罹患膽結石<ref name=WS2016/>，然後使用[[超音波|超音波]]確診<ref name=NIH2013/>，併發症也可從血液檢查中發現<ref name=NIH2013/>。

<!-- Prevention and treatment -->
預防膽結石的方式有保持健康體重、高纖飲食和降低[[單醣|單醣]]的攝取<ref name=NIH2013/>。當有病徵才需要治療<ref name=NIH2013/>。治療方式一般建議{{le|膽囊去除術|Cholecystectomy|手術去除膽囊}}<ref name=NIH2013/>，可以由{{le|腹腔鏡手術|aparoscopic surgery|幾個小切口}}或由單個較大的切口完成<ref name=NIH2013/>。手術通常在{{le|全身麻醉|General anaesthesia}}下完成<ref name=NIH2013/>。無法進行手術的人，會嘗試用藥物來溶解石塊或{{le|超音波震碎|Lithotripsy}}<ref name=NIH2013/>。

<!-- Epidemiology and prognosis -->
已開發國家中，10-15％的成年人患有膽結石<ref name=WS2016>{{cite journal|last1=Ansaloni|first1=L|title=2016 WSES guidelines on acute calculous cholecystitis.|journal=World journal of emergency surgery : WJES|date=2016|volume=11|pages=25|pmid=27307785|doi=10.1186/s13017-016-0082-5|pmc=4908702}}</ref>，然而，非洲許多地區的發生率低至3%<ref>{{cite book|last1=editors|first1=Ronnie A. Rosenthal, Michael E. Zenilman, Mark R. Katlic,|title=Principles and practice of geriatric surgery|date=2011|publisher=Springer|location=Berlin|isbn=9781441969996|page=944|edition=2nd|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=VcgmpMZE6a8C&pg=PA944|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160815224542/https://books.google.ca/books?id=VcgmpMZE6a8C&pg=PA944|archivedate=2016-08-15|df=}}</ref>。2013年膽囊和膽道相關疾病盛行人數約1.04億人（1.6％），造成106,000人死亡<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Global Burden of Disease Study 2013|first1=Collaborators|title=Global, regional, and national incidence, prevalence, and years lived with disability for 301 acute and chronic diseases and injuries in 188 countries, 1990-2013: a systematic analysis for the Global Burden of Disease Study 2013.|journal=Lancet|date=22 August 2015|volume=386|issue=9995|pages=743–800|pmid=26063472|doi=10.1016/s0140-6736(15)60692-4|pmc=4561509}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=GBD 2013 Mortality and Causes of Death|first1=Collaborators|title=Global, regional, and national age-sex specific all-cause and cause-specific mortality for 240 causes of death, 1990-2013: a systematic analysis for the Global Burden of Disease Study 2013.|journal=Lancet|date=10 January 2015|volume=385|issue=9963|pages=117–71|pmid=25530442|doi=10.1016/s0140-6736(14)61682-2|pmc=4340604}}</ref>。女性比男性常出現膽結石的情形，而且在40歲以後更常見<ref name=NIH2013/>。種族也影響了膽結石發生率<ref name=NIH2013/>，例如，48％的[[美國印第安人|美國印第安人]]有膽結石<ref name=NIH2013/>病人在執行膽囊切除手術後，一般而言結果都很好<ref name=NIH2013/>。
